title: Fnatic getting booed after beating BJK

replies.body: How TSM still has fans is just baffling to me.
LoL the downvotes on this thread.  No need for saltiness... loser NA fans :)

I was in the audience, and we started chanting for BJK because we had already known they lost at champion select. And the fact that they locked in Bard.

One of my friends was like, "Why are we BMing Fnatic? They got so close to beating SKT and got no recognition for it."
There wasn't much boo-ing. It was more BJK chanting.
